Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.90,0:00:05.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Got it?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.02,0:00:06.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.61,0:00:07.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.53,0:00:11.94,Default,,0,0,0,,It's really blurry.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.36,0:00:15.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Rin-chan! Kouki! Stand beside each other!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.24,0:00:17.87,Default,,0,0,0,,All right!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.87,0:00:19.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Kouki-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.83,0:00:23.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Here goes.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.67,0:00:30.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay. Next, I'll get a photo of you and Rin-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.84,0:00:32.05,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't need to get one of me.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.05,0:00:33.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course I do!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.51,0:00:35.76,Default,,0,0,0,,She'll grow up before you know it.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.76,0:00:37.55,Default,,0,0,0,,You need to keep a record of these moments.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.64,0:00:39.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.10,0:00:45.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Daikichi-san, try to relax a little.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.42,0:02:42.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Not again!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.22,0:02:51.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Rin! How many times have I told you not to go wandering off on your own?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.15,0:02:52.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.77,0:02:54.37,Default,,0,0,0,,You're a big girl now.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.37,0:02:55.98,Default,,0,0,0,,You have to get it together.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.98,0:02:57.24,Default,,0,0,0,,I know...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.49,0:02:59.95,Default,,0,0,0,,You clearly don't!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.95,0:03:02.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Daikichi, can we buy this for a snack?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.66,0:03:05.16,Default,,0,0,0,,A snack?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.95,0:03:08.75,Default,,0,0,0,,It just looked really good...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.96,0:03:14.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Have you never had cereal before?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.04,0:03:17.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Nope. I wonder if it's too much for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.96,0:03:20.17,Default,,0,0,0,,No, I don't mind buying it, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.72,0:03:23.59,Default,,0,0,0,,You're really supposed to eat that for breakfast.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.14,0:03:26.64,Default,,0,0,0,,It's okay to have sweets for a meal?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.64,0:03:30.10,Default,,0,0,0,,How should I put this? It looks like sweets,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.39,0:03:32.44,Default,,0,0,0,,but it's okay to have it at meal times.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.44,0:03:34.15,Default,,0,0,0,,You put milk on it, and...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.15,0:03:35.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.23,0:03:38.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe you can have it for breakfast tomorrow?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.32,0:03:40.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Yep, I will!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.07,0:03:41.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you want some too, Daikichi?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.07,0:03:44.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Nah. I don't feel like I've had a proper breakfast after I've had cereal.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.83,0:03:48.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Put the cereal in here.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.74,0:03:50.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.04,0:03:55.00,Default,,0,0,0,,You're really bad at that, Daikichi.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.00,0:03:57.17,Default,,0,0,0,,My hands are too dry.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.17,0:03:58.67,Default,,0,0,0,,You're like an old man.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.67,0:04:02.26,Note,,0,0,0,,TL Note: The line Daikichi uses here is from Mitokoumon, a Japanese TV drama centering around Tokugawa Mitsukuni, a prominent figure in Japanese history.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.67,0:03:59.80,Default,,0,0,0,,"Bite your tongue, knave!"
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.80,0:04:02.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah! Mitokoumon!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.26,0:04:09.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Daikichi, there are cherry blossoms down here. Let's go back this way.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.56,0:04:10.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.14,0:04:13.56,Default,,0,0,0,,They're blooming everywhere, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.56,0:04:15.23,Default,,0,0,0,,The warm weather brings them out.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.77,0:04:19.86,Default,,0,0,0,,It's huge...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.86,0:04:21.19,Default,,0,0,0,,It's in full bloom.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.70,0:04:26.70,Default,,0,0,0,,How about we plant something to\Ncommemorate you starting junior school?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.70,0:04:27.66,Default,,0,0,0,,"Commemorate"?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.20,0:04:30.62,Default,,0,0,0,,It's sort of like a memory.{I just sort of like a memory}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.50,0:04:35.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Every year, you and the tree would grow together.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.83,0:04:37.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.21,0:04:40.09,Default,,0,0,0,,I have a tree, too, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.09,0:04:41.42,Default,,0,0,0,,At your house?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.42,0:04:42.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Near my parents'.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.88,0:04:46.39,Default,,0,0,0,,When I was born, they planted a fragrant olive tree,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.39,0:04:49.31,Default,,0,0,0,,and Kazumi got a tea olive tree.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.31,0:04:51.68,Default,,0,0,0,,A fragrant olive tree? Is that the one that smells really good?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.68,0:04:53.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, that's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.02,0:04:55.06,Default,,0,0,0,,I've never heard of a tea olive tree.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.06,0:04:59.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Its flowers and scent are a lot more plain than the fragrant olive.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.82,0:05:03.07,Default,,0,0,0,,So Kazumi always made a fuss over how it wasn't fair...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.07,0:05:05.66,Default,,0,0,0,,...and tore the flowers off mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.11,0:05:10.87,Default,,0,0,0,,And when I said I'd trade, she said she didn't want some stupid second-hand tree.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.45,0:05:14.21,Default,,0,0,0,,On second thoughts, that wasn't a good memory at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.21,0:05:16.33,Default,,0,0,0,,So why am I wanting to do the same thing for Rin?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.25,0:05:21.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Anyway, if we're going to plant a tree, it should have pretty flowers. That way, it'll be more fun when it blooms.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.71,0:05:23.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Or one with fruit you can eat.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.26,0:05:24.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah! I want a loquat!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.84,0:05:27.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Loquat?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.38,0:05:29.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, a loquat!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.81,0:05:35.73,Default,,0,0,0,,I already saved some loquat seeds.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.73,0:05:37.14,Default,,0,0,0,,You're going to grow it from a seed?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.27,0:05:40.02,Default,,0,0,0,,It'll be all you can eat loquats!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.02,0:05:41.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Assuming it'll actually grow.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.19,0:05:46.78,Default,,0,0,0,,To be honest, I was actually thinking of planting a tree about your size.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.78,0:05:48.07,Default,,0,0,0,,So a loquat's no good?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.20,0:05:52.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, a tree takes a lot longer to grow than\Nmorning-glories and other flowers like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.49,0:05:55.79,Note,,0,0,0,,TL Note: This is a Japanese proverb meaning that each thing will happen in its own time.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.49,0:05:55.79,Default,,0,0,0,,It's like they say: peaches take three years.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.79,0:05:57.62,Default,,0,0,0,,And persimmons take eight!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.62,0:05:59.83,Default,,0,0,0,,You really are Granddad's kid, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.83,0:06:01.50,Default,,0,0,0,,So how about loquats?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.50,0:06:05.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't really know, but what if it takes about ten years?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.92,0:06:07.43,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.80,0:06:11.39,Default,,0,0,0,,By then, you'll probably me more interested in fancy sweets.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.68,0:06:13.72,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't imagine that...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.72,0:06:15.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Daikichi, hurry up!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.39,0:06:19.69,Default,,0,0,0,,If we don't hurry, we won't be able to eat them for ages!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.69,0:06:21.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Right, right...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.48,0:06:25.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Is this enough?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.36,0:06:29.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah. If it's too deep, the bud won't be able to make it to the surface.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.24,0:06:30.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.75,0:06:39.54,Default,,0,0,0,,You really couldn't be more like Granddad.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.54,0:06:41.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's hope it comes out soon!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.79,0:06:42.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.75,0:06:46.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Rin, do you know about ninja?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.26,0:06:50.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah. Kouki-kun said he's going to be one.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.89,0:06:55.26,Default,,0,0,0,,They say ninja jump over a hemp tree every morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.26,0:07:00.48,Default,,0,0,0,,And the tree keeps growing bigger and bigger, so eventually they can jump massive heights.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.56,0:07:04.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Why don't you try that with a loquat tree?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.32,0:07:06.65,Default,,0,0,0,,I will!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.90,0:07:10.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.87,0:07:15.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.12,0:07:15.91,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.41,0:07:20.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, hey! How big does a loquat tree grow?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.79,0:07:22.42,Default,,0,0,0,,As high as the roof of our house?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.42,0:07:26.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Um, well... Yeah, probably about that high.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.89,0:07:36.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go back inside already.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.06,0:07:37.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Ten times more!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.60,0:07:43.31,Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder if it'll start growing tomorrow?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.31,0:07:45.40,Default,,0,0,0,,That's probably a bit early.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.98,0:07:48.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Got everything?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.36,0:07:49.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.69,0:07:50.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.90,0:07:56.03,Default,,0,0,0,,They told us to get someone at home to check our timetable, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.03,0:07:58.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Man, what a pain...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.99,0:08:02.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Nobody ever did this for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.75,0:08:06.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, she's right. It says I'm supposed to check it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.88,0:08:12.97,Default,,0,0,0,,A fire?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.97,0:08:14.84,Default,,0,0,0,,It's probably a police car.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.84,0:08:16.30,Default,,0,0,0,,There was a crime?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.30,0:08:17.39,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.72,0:08:21.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Daikichi, attach this whistle to my bag.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.61,0:08:28.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Rin...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.69,0:08:33.78,Default,,0,0,0,,If someone you don't know starts\Ntalking to you, blow this really hard.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.78,0:08:34.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.45,0:08:37.45,Default,,0,0,0,,And then run and hide in someone's house. It doesn't matter whose.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.45,0:08:38.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.16,0:08:39.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Or a store!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.70,0:08:40.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.92,0:08:52.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Rin! School!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.67,0:08:57.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Daikichi! Hurry up and get up! I'm going to be late!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.26,0:08:58.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Right...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.72,0:09:00.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's eat.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.35,0:09:00.56,Alt,,0,0,0,,Let's eat!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.18,0:09:02.81,Default,,0,0,0,,You put milk on it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.81,0:09:05.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Can't I just eat a little like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.69,0:09:06.90,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.40,0:09:14.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Pet dogs eat this too, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.40,0:09:17.78,Default,,0,0,0,,That's dog food! It's just for dogs!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.78,0:09:18.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.99,0:09:20.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.45,0:09:23.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Humans can't eat dog food.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.04,0:09:24.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Aw...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.58,0:09:26.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't look so disappointed.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.84,0:09:31.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it good?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.67,0:09:33.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Yep! It's yummy!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.88,0:09:35.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Rice balls are still my favourite, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.88,0:09:38.22,Default,,0,0,0,,It's going to take a lot to beat them, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.22,0:09:39.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Daikichi, your phone!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.68,0:09:40.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.23,0:09:46.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Good morning!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.06,0:09:50.15,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry, but Kouki was so excited that he just ran off to yours.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.52,0:09:53.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, no, it's fine. We're good to go.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.40,0:09:54.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.82,0:09:54.57,Alt,,0,0,0,,Rin-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.57,0:09:56.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Kouki-kun's here!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.90,0:09:56.61,Alt,,0,0,0,,Rin-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.24,0:09:57.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, here he is.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.33,0:10:02.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Yo!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.91,0:10:05.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Kouki-kun, you're covered in sticky willows!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.79,0:10:08.87,Default,,0,0,0,,You look like you've been living in the bushes like some wild animal.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.87,0:10:10.46,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not an animal!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.75,0:10:13.05,Default,,0,0,0,,And what's with your hair?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.05,0:10:15.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Rin, go get a comb.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.01,0:10:16.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.30,0:10:22.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Geez... Your backpack is all torn, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.89,0:10:27.39,Default,,0,0,0,,And I bet you've been scraping that stick along people's fences, too, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.81,0:10:29.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you a psychic?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.23,0:10:31.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Anyone could see that by just looking at you!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.36,0:10:34.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you sure it's not because you did it as a kid, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.90,0:10:36.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Rin, you should be getting ready!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.57,0:10:38.32,Default,,0,0,0,,I know!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.32,0:10:40.61,Default,,0,0,0,,What's that look for?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.83,0:10:45.87,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going now!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.66,0:10:49.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, wait! Wait there a seco{\fscx300}-
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.38,0:10:52.33,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.96,0:11:01.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Kouki-kun! Don't keep blowing it when there's nothing wrong!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.55,0:11:03.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Kouki-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.22,0:11:07.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! Quit blowing that!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.52,0:11:10.39,Default,,0,0,0,,If you keep blowing it, nobody's going to come help when you're really in trouble!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.85,0:11:13.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Understood?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.07,0:11:17.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Go on, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.15,0:11:20.20,Default,,0,0,0,,See you later!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.91,0:11:25.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Be careful of cars!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.08,0:11:25.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.00,0:11:38.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Kouki-kun...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.76,0:11:40.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go this way.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.51,0:11:42.43,Default,,0,0,0,,We're not supposed to take detours.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.43,0:11:45.55,Default,,0,0,0,,This isn't a detour. It's a short-cut.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.39,0:11:49.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Ninjas...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.93,0:11:52.60,Default,,0,0,0,,...always use paths like this!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.19,0:11:54.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Geez...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.86,0:12:01.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow, it winds back and forth!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.57,0:12:02.11,Default,,0,0,0,,I know, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.09,0:12:24.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Kouki-kun! Hurry up!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.30,0:12:27.60,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no point taking a short cut if you're going to be slow!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.10,0:12:34.56,Default,,0,0,0,,That's not when you're supposed to blow it!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.03,0:12:47.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Kouki-kun...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.76,0:13:09.72,Default,,0,0,0,,That kid is a real piece of work...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.72,0:13:10.93,Default,,0,0,0,,I know, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.43,0:13:14.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Though, to be honest...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.02,0:13:16.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Most boys are like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.81,0:13:18.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Daikichi...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.44,0:13:22.78,Default,,0,0,0,,You should keep the ninja training to jumping over the loquat tree.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.78,0:13:23.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Exactly!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.66,0:13:29.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.74,0:13:34.58,Default,,0,0,0,,That loquat tree is in commemoration of me starting school, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.58,0:13:35.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.83,0:13:38.58,Default,,0,0,0,,But your fragrant olive tree was planted when you were born.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.58,0:13:41.80,Default,,0,0,0,,So it's a little different, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.84,0:13:46.26,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess I don't have anything like that...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.84,0:13:49.22,Default,,0,0,0,,You're so smart...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.93,0:13:53.68,Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder if her mum bothered to plant a tree for her or anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.18,0:13:58.02,Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder if there's one at Granddad's.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.02,0:14:00.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, yeah, Granddad might've...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.69,0:14:03.57,Default,,0,0,0,,But you weren't told anything about something like that, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.57,0:14:04.78,Default,,0,0,0,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.45,0:14:09.70,Default,,0,0,0,,And Granddad's gone now.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.49,0:14:14.91,Default,,0,0,0,,If I don't know about it, nobody does.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.20,0:14:19.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I shouldn't have told her about my olive tree.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.04,0:14:23.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Daikichi! Your elbow's on the table again!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.46,0:14:25.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Right! Sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.44,0:14:39.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Shit...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.52,0:14:45.86,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't think we'd be meeting again.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.40,0:14:49.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Neither did I.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.99,0:14:56.95,Default,,0,0,0,,This is from the entrance ceremony.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.95,0:14:58.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.54,0:15:01.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? A tree for Rin?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.50,0:15:07.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah! There is! There was!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.13,0:15:08.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.17,0:15:11.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Y-Yes, well... I think there was one...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.97,0:15:14.22,Default,,0,0,0,,How can you not be sure?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.93,0:15:17.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Souichi-san was the one who planted it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.10,0:15:19.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Granddad...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.11,0:15:28.61,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd like to replant it at my place.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.19,0:15:30.82,Default,,0,0,0,,What sort of tree is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.82,0:15:32.49,Default,,0,0,0,,A small one.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.49,0:15:34.74,Default,,0,0,0,,No, I mean... What type was it?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.74,0:15:36.08,Default,,0,0,0,,And the place.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.54,0:15:39.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Um... It's still small.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.37,0:15:42.00,Default,,0,0,0,,And the branches are thin.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.92,0:15:44.13,Default,,0,0,0,,It's here.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.88,0:15:48.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you really draw for a living?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.80,0:15:52.68,Default,,0,0,0,,I draw manga, not maps.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.68,0:15:54.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Which way is north?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.55,0:15:55.55,Default,,0,0,0,,North?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.55,0:15:57.89,Default,,0,0,0,,The sun rises in the west, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.89,0:15:59.73,Default,,0,0,0,,You've got it the wrong way round!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.48,0:16:04.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Forget the directions. Just draw me one side of the street in front of the house.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.40,0:16:06.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, I see. That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.11,0:16:12.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Anyway, I have work, so I have to go.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.03,0:16:13.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks for the food.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.11,0:16:16.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry to bother you at such a busy time.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.30,0:16:40.60,Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder if I had a tree.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.60,0:16:44.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Granddad would have planted something for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.44,0:16:46.27,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sure of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.73,0:16:52.24,Default,,0,0,0,,And if he didn't, all you need to do is plant another one.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.86,0:16:54.61,Default,,0,0,0,,One that's six years old.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.36,0:16:56.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.45,0:16:58.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Would you like to see Daikichi's tree?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.83,0:17:01.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I want to see!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.33,0:17:05.25,Default,,0,0,0,,It's really big, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.25,0:17:07.92,Default,,0,0,0,,It's thirty years old, after all. Just like Daikichi.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.92,0:17:10.92,Default,,0,0,0,,They've both gotten so big...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.92,0:17:13.51,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a fragrant olive, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.51,0:17:15.88,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right. I'm surprised you recognised it!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.88,0:17:16.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Daikichi told me.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.80,0:17:19.68,Default,,0,0,0,,This one is Kazumi's.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.68,0:17:20.68,Default,,0,0,0,,A tea olive?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.06,0:17:22.10,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.77,0:17:28.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you remember the big tree in Granddad's back garden?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.44,0:17:29.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, that one?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.95,0:17:39.28,Default,,0,0,0,,That's my tree. A tea olive.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.28,0:17:40.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.41,0:17:47.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? This tree...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.92,0:17:52.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Granddad planted it for me when I was born.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.22,0:18:01.68,Default,,0,0,0,,That's the same tree as Kazumi-oneechan!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.97,0:18:03.39,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.35,0:18:08.60,Default,,0,0,0,,When I was young, I always compared my height with it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.06,0:18:12.77,Default,,0,0,0,,I really loved that tree, so I decided to\Nplant another one for my daughter here.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.48,0:18:16.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Was that a tea olive tree?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.36,0:18:19.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Did Daikichi compare his height with his tree, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.45,0:18:20.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.62,0:18:26.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.08,0:18:31.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Long before the day we met...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.25,0:18:33.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Daikichi, is that...?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.34,0:18:36.09,Default,,0,0,0,,The leaves are the same!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.97,0:18:39.05,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a six year old fragrant olive.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.05,0:18:40.93,Default,,0,0,0,,The same as mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.73,0:18:49.77,Default,,0,0,0,,That's us done.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.77,0:18:51.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, I forgot!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.48,0:18:52.69,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.69,0:18:55.15,Default,,0,0,0,,It looks like I won't be able to jump over this one.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.69,0:18:58.24,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't think I could, either.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.88,0:19:22.18,Default,,0,0,0,,We didn't even know about Rin half a year ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.18,0:19:23.85,Default,,0,0,0,,I know...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.85,0:19:27.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Daikichi! The train's going to leave!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.18,0:19:28.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Coming!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.10,0:19:29.98,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd better go.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.77,0:19:32.69,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll see you to the station.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.19,0:19:36.15,Default,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.19,0:19:41.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Long before the day we met,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.71,0:19:55.13,Default,,0,0,0,,we were already drops in the same river.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.73,0:21:37.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Daikichi!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.52,0:21:39.11,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.90,0:21:40.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Daikichi!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.11,0:21:41.82,Default,,0,0,0,,What happened?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.53,0:21:43.74,Alt,,0,0,0,,Kouki-kun...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.82,0:21:43.74,Default,,0,0,0,,There's some weird old guy outside!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.74,0:21:45.90,Alt,,0,0,0,,No, he's just...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.74,0:21:45.90,Default,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.90,0:21:47.36,Alt,,0,0,0,,Daikichi, it's not like that...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.90,0:21:47.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Where is he?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.82,0:21:50.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Jeez, listen to me already you guys!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.45,0:21:53.75,Default,,0,0,0,,That's Matsui-san! He's our neighbour!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.12,0:21:56.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't call him "some weird old guy"!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.37,0:22:00.17,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.34,0:22:07.09,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm... So... rry...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.43,0:22:08.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Not at all. It's my fault.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.68,0:22:12.56,Default,,0,0,0,,It seems I gave you quite a scare when I called out to you like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.01,0:22:14.81,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.81,0:22:17.56,Default,,0,0,0,,No, we've been terribly rude...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.56,0:22:20.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Take care on your way to school.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.31,0:22:21.77,Default,,0,0,0,,See you later!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.70,0:22:29.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.74,0:22:33.99,Default,,0,0,0,,When you ran away, you took Rin with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.99,0:22:37.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? But Kouki-kun made a mistake.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.46,0:22:40.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I can rest a little easier knowing Kouki's around.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.92,0:22:42.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Just a little?!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.13,0:22:44.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course! You're still just a little kid!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.25,0:22:46.51,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not a kid!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.41,0:22:50.93,Default,,0,0,0,,We're going to be late...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.93,0:22:56.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Good afternoon. Rin here.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.06,0:22:59.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you want to hear a scary story?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.19,0:23:04.28,Default,,0,0,0,,The skeleton of the science room walks to the music room at night.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.86,0:23:08.86,Default,,0,0,0,,There he plays "who laughs first" with Beethoven. {niramekko is a game where you keep watching to the other person's face, until someone laughs}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.74,0:23:14.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Reina-chan told me that inside a really dark futon.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.04,0:23:16.20,Default,,0,0,0,,After that, she told the adults too.
